id="link-id19cbaba0" name="link-id19cbaba0">Processor</a> family
paths in the product portfolio graph (data network) unveil a lot
more about <a href=
"http://linkeddata.uriburner.com/about/html/http://www.openlinksw.com/dataspace/organization/openlink%23this"
id="link-ide9b7070" name="link-ide9b7070">OpenLink Software</a>
