"margin: 1em; float: right; display: block;"><a href=
"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Image:ChristmasCrackers.jpg"><img src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/c/cb/ChristmasCrackers.jpg/202px-ChristmasCrackers.jpg"
