<li class="zemanta-article-ul-li"><a href=
"http://www.linux.com/feature/144853">Nepomuk and KDE to introduce
the semantic desktop</a></li>
<li class="zemanta-article-ul-li"><a href=
"http://battellemedia.com/archives/004658.php">On Speech Based
Interfaces to Search - and Beyond</a></li>
</ul>
